{"tid":1033262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大灣區中的廢柴]垃圾廢老返大陸又要怕稅重","createTime":"2019-02-23T03:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T08:41:30.000Z","uid":14256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b038506fc7b529c01844215f52e82a3aba7bb225","tid":1033262,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"你老幾呀而家，又要返大陸又要人地益你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全反映到班廢老一事無成，無實幹，咁耐以黎淨係識得利用香港地理環境既優勢黎R著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁愛國點解唔交返大陸稅率呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/8ZE0YR?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2F8ZE0YR%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1A5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=1dbee77d\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/8ZE0YR?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n//政制及內地事務局長聶德權在本台節目表示，中央清楚知道港人關注在內地生活的稅率問題，指當局會探討每個相關議題，包括港人按本港稅率在內地納稅的「港人港稅」安排，強調政府「不會封後門」，但認為社會要設身處地思考，若港人在內地工作，享受內地福利，但就按本港稅率納稅，是否完全適合。他又指，若果有個別城市希望招攬人才，可以透過吸引人才政策，讓公司或政府為相關人才提供稅務補貼。<br />\n<br />\n至於規劃綱要提出，研究開展非急重病人跨境陸路轉運服務，聶德權表示，隨著大灣區發展，會有更多港人北上學習、就業或退休，他們對醫療服務有一定需求，而且對於本港醫療較有信心，認為這項建議能夠改善現有轉運安排，製造更便利的環境，強調政府會先照顧本地醫療需求。<br />\n<br />\nSee detail<br />\n聶德權：本港可自行決定落實大灣區規劃(商台新聞)<br />\n<br />\nSee detail<br />\n聶德權指政府會探討港人港稅安排 (商台新聞 馮天蘭攝)"},{"pid":"aa91f4caf4c6df51755e45fab6d735eb85d9cc15","tid":1033262,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"五毛呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c9448de3385131be6ab6c3091aeb885959f10e","tid":1033262,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:32:54.000Z","msg":"五毛不願面對"},{"pid":"a9f56d4860cbd85cf01859a80fa9fd3c35e7a533","tid":1033262,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:34:02.000Z","msg":"咁愛國<br />\n但又唔肯同党和国家共享財富<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8602bcda0c997ff21d2b6b8436b0f718fba49130","tid":1033262,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:38:05.000Z","msg":"你係咪中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13767be978b607174968d1472b45369adca13328","tid":1033262,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8602bcda0c997ff21d2b6b8436b0f718fba49130","tid":1033262,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:38:05.000Z","msg":"你係咪中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:24:22.000Z","msg":"你係咪俾大陸稅呀中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33470b09b45f9ce89b8a37fc036e67c61e094d4f","tid":1033262,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T07:15:55.000Z","msg":"五毛唔敢出聲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9895ab46434f8d2321b9a4988cec0dd2c90628","tid":1033262,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T08:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face